ru.yandex.yandexmapkit.map
Class MapLayer

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--ru.yandex.yandexmapkit.map.MapLayer
public class MapLayer
extends java.lang.Object

MapLayer.java: Map layer. Layers can be visible, e.g. map types (MAP, SATELLITE, PUBLIC) or invisible, e.g. bus stops or various map features.

This file is a part of the Yandex Map Kit.
